#
# Release notes 1.7.6
#

Updaters from 1.7 release can just update the packages and restart
all services.

Updates from earlier releases require manual steps afterwards, 
please check the README.UPDATERS file for details.

Changes since 1.7.5 release
===========================

Changes:

* OBS can be used also together with Rails 2.3.8 now
* Updated default targets in webui, according to current api.opensuse.org state

Fixes:

* Fix permission check on storing request data, it was
  possible to overwrite request data in some circumstances.

